Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.90,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.80,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.40,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你救救Candy吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 如果能救的话 我肯定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生你应该可以治好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy对我来说可是唯一的家人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上 马上医生就会治好你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 请你救救Candy吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 拜托你不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我一个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.00,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}听不到的叫声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 会是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯子以前就想要一只小狗了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.80,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.70,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜 才十岁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯子 差不多该走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 我们两个要一起努力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.80,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.60,0:04:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 我以后该怎么办好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯子 晚饭要凉了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放在这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本条医生 不得了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木先生的小狗碰到交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿部骨折了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就带来 刚来了电话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那只狗就交给你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.10,0:05:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在必须得去给小泉老师的狗看病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨折这种小事 自然就能好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5点要给Puruto注射可别忘了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.90,0:05:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女演员的狗如果死了就麻烦了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关本小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 Candy的事还是要感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那个时候有点惊慌失措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有好好向你道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好外出诊察了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我会帮你传达给医生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么样 精神有没有恢复了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 不过还是不习惯独自一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.80,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一直闷闷不乐也不是个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.60,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我想Candy应该是很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到本条医生这么好的医生最后的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请您代我向医生问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才帮你打了止痛剂 马上就不会难受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我一个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关本小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 把你叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 反正在家也没什么事做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 要和我说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.00,0:07:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 其实在那个时候议员河合先生打电话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高尔夫吗 我是没问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是给河合先生添麻烦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 没什么没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我 还是河合先生您5号洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那杆攻果岭真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我真的是碰巧啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是运气好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.30,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月底的星期二吧 我正好有空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 完全没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.60,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那Candy不是没有接受任何诊治吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话挂断后虽然进行了治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那时已经太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我要是强行挂断电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是道歉就能受到你的原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到纯子你之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在不忍心隐瞒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那间诊所就是那样的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它那么痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了这种电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 一定是骗人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅 纯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有带你去看那种医生就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的灵异特别节目看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超恐怖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你知道地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零点登录的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能帮你消除怨恨的那个网页吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说部林高中里真的有人试过哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信 地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.60,0:10:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 有邮件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 快连上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你是地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.90,0:11:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.90,0:11:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开这个就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.30,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是你死之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开这根红线的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.30,0:12:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨就能消除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到 办不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我吧 Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy那么痛苦地死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来 是一起巨额渎职事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本台朝丸新闻的记者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采访了处于本事件焦点的那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有证据啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己承认怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了那种事 以为会被原谅吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.10,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要有证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有哪家电视台可以报道那个医生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.00,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个诊所有很多政治家和名人经常光顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种言论就算通过媒体流传出去也会马上被抹杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样的话Candy它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是Candy 还有其他的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个医生无法原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是信任他才把宠物带去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 关本小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.90,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很暗 要注意脚下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 这只狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交通事故中脚骨折了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上手术的话 就不会这么严重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 还是抓紧时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十点还不离开这里 本条就要回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查病历没用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.90,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都重新改过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还是过来帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.50,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他冒充使用了高价药并向客人收费
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库存可能与清单不符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿米拖尔（一种镇静剂）7箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对 是7箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.80,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 完全相符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我都从关本小姐那里听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy那么痛苦 你还打高尔夫球电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你从关本那里听说了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy 我可是尽全力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy是被你杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你的所作所为全部在媒体前公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.40,0:15:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 所以跑来寻找证据吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 找到证据了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.80,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有证据就不要说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是问问当事者怎么样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.60,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 我是个那么坏的医生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么我可听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说清楚点让我听懂吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过分 太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么想说的就说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 我已经受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说它们或许是单纯的赚钱工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对于大家都是重要的宠物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Candy更是纯子唯一的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条脏狗还当做家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只是这附近捡来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种狗跑来只会把医院弄脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄的臭气熏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.50,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种狗 为了医院也应该早点死比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我就放过你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是下次再听到你们奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就告你们诽谤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你还能在这行混饭吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说早点死比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.80,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅 不能原谅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.40,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.50,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 长衫放好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只为了条狗 这么晚还把我叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好敲你一笔的 给我记住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那种地方跑出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨头断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可又是个撞得厉害的车祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他抬出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我的腿骨折了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帮我治啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了吗 昨天的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个漂亮的全垒打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球的事情怎么都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快点治我的腿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是暗号失误吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.10,0:19:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那球可是投向正中央的直线球啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.30,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不管病人的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.40,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闲聊了 快替我治疗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么弯起胳膊一挥 球就飞出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说棒球的事情怎样都好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点治我的腿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 这种球我也可以打出全垒打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有听我讲话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你们了 求你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看看我的腿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 开始手术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里的问题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是啊 病人的话都听不懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.10,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚啊 腿骨折了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就从随便切开来看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们准备切哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里 是腿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿受伤了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.60,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.80,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己的所作所为有所悔悟了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说动物或许只是赚钱工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对于爱护他们人就相当于家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.70,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不也是跟我一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们穿上奇怪的衣服 带着它们参加聚会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们当作炫耀自己身份的工具而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有我要受这种痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有什么错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说呢 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带我去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.30,0:21:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生 我好痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.30,0:21:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要过来 不要过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.40,0:22:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关本小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.10,0:22:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来送我了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你要回乡下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.50,0:22:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 倒是我该向你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.30,0:22:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呢 乡下也能找到和动物相关的工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.70,0:22:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10点9分开往福冈的希望号马上就要发车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.60,0:22:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一找到工作我就会告诉你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.60,0:22:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.90,0:22:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈 Candy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到你们虽然感觉很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.50,0:22:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会继续努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.70,0:22:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请你们在天上保佑我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.30,0:22:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
